PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FITV News reporter Tim Scott visited St
OL,8,FPauls Primary School who are using the
OL,9,FMarcus Rashford mural to learn about
OL,10,Fstanding up to racism.
OL,12,FA primary school is using Marcus
OL,13,FRashford as a lesson in how to stand
OL,14,Fup to racism and online hate.
OL,16,FPupils at St Pauls Primary in
OL,17,FWithington, south Manchester, have
OL,18,Fbeen learning about the Euros in 2021,
OL,19,Fwhich saw Rashford and other black
OL,20,FEngland players subject to racist
OL,21,Fabuse for missing penalties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FBut after the mural of Rashford in the
OL,8,Fsuburb was defaced after England's
OL,9,Floss, people began spontaneously
OL,10,Fcovering the damage with messages of
OL,11,Fsupport and solidarity.
OL,13,FThe tributes were later archived and
OL,14,Fdigitised by Manchester libraries, and
OL,15,Fhave now been made into a teaching
OL,16,Fpack for schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FHolly Snowden a teacher at St Pauls
OL,8,FPrimary said her students are engaging
OL,9,Fwell with the resource as it is more
OL,10,Frelatable than their normal history
OL,11,Fclasses.
OL,13,FShe said: "With our regular history
OL,14,Flessons, sometimes the topics are way
OL,15,Fout of their reach, they're so far
OL,16,Fback in history that it doesn't mean
OL,17,Fas much to them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,F"With this resource, it's something
OL,8,Fthat happened within their community
OL,9,Fand it's quite recent history, so
OL,10,Fthey're really connecting with it, and
OL,11,Fit's giving them a sense of belonging
OL,12,Fin their community."
OL,14,FThe teaching pack includes videos and
OL,15,Fspaces for children to leave their own
OL,16,Fcomments. They can also click on the
OL,17,Fdigitised messages of support that
OL,18,Fwere left at the mural to find out
OL,19,Fmore about them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
