FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FSome students from St Pauls Primary
OL,8,Fvisited the mural, which is on the
OL,9,Fwall of The Coffee House Cafe.
OL,11,FOne student said: "We learned that
OL,12,Feven though Marcus Rashford faced
OL,13,Fabuse, he pushed through and the
OL,14,Fvillage of Withington stood together.
OL,15,FFrom this we learned everybody is more
OL,16,Fpowerful together, and stronger as a
OL,17,Fteam."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FAnother student said: "We have learned
OL,8,Fthat cities came together to show that
OL,9,Fthey believed in Marcus and wanted him
OL,10,Fto keep going even though people were
OL,11,Fbeing mean to him."
OL,13,FThe mural is looked after by
OL,14,FWithington Walls, a community art
OL,15,Fgroup that helped put the teaching
OL,16,Fpack together.
OL,18,FEd Wellard, from Withington Walls,
OL,19,Fsaid: "I think it's really exciting,
OL,20,Fit's a really important story that
OL,21,Fneeds to be preserved and shared.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,F"The educational resource is an
OL,8,Famazing opportunity for parents and
OL,9,Fteachers to revisit that story: What
OL,10,Fhappened when the mural was created,
OL,11,Fwhat happened after Euros, spark those
OL,12,Fdiscussions about racism, community,
OL,13,Fhaving empathy and standing up for
OL,14,Feach other."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
