PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,FManchester City Libraries archive
OL,8,Fofficer Jenny Marsden said: "When the
OL,9,Fcollection first came to the archive,
OL,10,Fwe saw how inspiring it was, and we
OL,11,Fthought it would be a really good
OL,12,Fcollection to work with children
OL,13,Fbecause we're always trying to engage
OL,14,Fchildren with the work in the
OL,15,Farchives, so it seemed a really good
OL,16,Ffit."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
