OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772193823
OL,3,CSchool using Marcus Rashford as a
OL,4,Clesson to stand up to racism and
OL,5,Conline hate
OL,7,F"We saw the events as a really
OL,8,Fsignificant moment in Manchester's
OL,9,Fhistory, and as the city's archive
OL,10,Fservice, we needed to collect and
OL,11,Farchive these significant moments as
OL,12,Fbest we can.
OL,14,F"We're trying to represent the history
OL,15,Fof the city as widely as possible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
